<HEAD>Eds: SUBS Bavier item to CORRECT age to 86 sted 87.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>Frances Bavier</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>SILER CITY, N.C. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Frances Bavier, remembered by millions
of fans as the devoted Aunt Bee on television's ``The Andy Griffith
Show,'' died Wednesday at age 86.
   A native of New York City, she appeared on Broadway in such
productions as ``Kiss and Tell,'' ``Point of No Return'' and ``The
