<TEXT>
   Here are the pronunciations of the names
of leading figures in Chile's presidential election:
   AUGUSTO PINOCHET _ ow-GOOSE-toh peen-oh-CHET.
   PATRICIO AYLWIN _ pah-TREE-shee-oh AISLE-ween.
   HERNAN BUCHI _ ehr-NAHN BEE-chee.
   FRANCISCO ERRAZURIZ _ frahn-SEES-koh eh-RAS-oo-ris.
</TEXT>
