<TEXT>
   five-year court battle with his former wife, a fundamentalist
Christian, for custody of his son. June 26, age 42.
</TEXT>
<NOTE>MICHAEL BENNETT@ _ Theatrical wunderkind who danced his way out</NOTE>
<TEXT>
   of the chorus line to become Broadway's most influential
